Title: Chimera face painting
Hours: By appointment
Description: I love using my face painting skills to help children transform into their most beloved characters! I am a local artist and designer of over 15 years experience and have been face painting for over three years. I use only Wolfe Arts face paints which are world renowned or their highly-pigmented Hydrocolor line of professional water-activated make-up. They are easy to remove and yet have the ability to stay fresh and in place for the day! I paint faces for school events, birthday parties, community events, grand openings and even have some adults that get in on the fun when I paint for family friendly office parties or other corporate events! I come dressed in character when requested which makes it even more fun for the kids! I love being around kids and my favorite part of what i do is seeing the wide eyed wonder on the faces I paint as they get to be transformed into the character of their choice!

Hours: Mon. - Sun.: 9:00 AM - 5:30 PM
Description:
Mix Bake Decorate Cake Shop loves working directly with their clients to create a custom cake that reflects their style, budget, event, and guest list. We'd love to work on your cake! 

We Also do custom Cupcakes, Cake Pops, Cookies, Gourmet Dessert Shots, Dessert Tables, and decorating parties and classes for all ages!

Each and every order is completely customized to what your specifications. From your initial consultation to the first moment when you slice into your tasty treat, we're happy to work with you to finalize every last detail. Below you'll find all the information you need to start planning your cake or other desserts.

In an initial meeting in person, over the phone or by email, your event details, flavour options, budget, and design ideas are discussed. If you want we will set up a cake tasting once the basics are covered for a small extra fee of $20.00. Cake sketches are reviewed, final design is approved and a deposit of 50% is required to save the date. One week prior to your event date, the remaining 50% deposit is required. Based on your contract, we will arrange to drop off your cake or other desserts at your event and make sure that it is picture perfect or we can set up a meeting place for you to pick up your order.

All pricing is based on design and varies for each cake or dessert. If you have pictures or a design you would like, please send me the pictures with how many people you will need to feed and I can give you an exact price.
